data.description: ***ASSUMABLE VA MORTGAGE!!!! YOU DO NOT HAVE TO BE A VETERAN TO ASSUME THIS MORTGAGE!! WELL BELOW MARKET INTEREST RATE AND NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED BY LENDER.  CALL FOR ALL THE GREAT DETAILS!!!*** Wow! Financing opportunity plus a fabulous  home in Southbay Yacht & Racquet Club with its own Marina! If you are looking for a vibrant community for you and your boat this is it! Activities for all ages including pickle ball, tennis, bocce ball, heated community pool, playground, clubs, scheduled events & more. Deep water marina with dock slips for almost every size boat, personal water craft and even a kayak launch and storage.  Recently renovated clubhouse with fitness center, ballroom, card room, meeting rooms and more. This well cared for home has had many updates and upgrades. ROOF 5.5 YEARS OLD, NEW ELECTRICAL PANEL 2.5 YEARS OLD, POOL RESURFACED, POOL PUMP 1 YEAR OLD, SPA UPDATED 5.5 YEARS AGO, TWO A/C UNITS NEW 2 YEARS AGO. ONE UNIT IS A HEAT PUMP, THE SECOND IS AN A/C UNIT. BOTH WITH REMAINDER OF 10 YEAR WARRANTY. PLUMBING WAS RECENTLY BROUGHT UP TO THE MOST RECENT CODES, NEW IRRIGATION, RAINMAKER SYSTEM RECENTLY INSTALLED, MANY NEW AND UNIQUE LIGHT FIXTURES AND FANS THROUGHOUT. SOME NEW PAINTING. BATHS HAVE BEEN REMODELED, NEW TRAVERTINE AND ENGINEERED HARDWOOD. Other features of the home include guest bath with a second shower outside! A very unique feature! 2nd and 3rd bedroom with an abundance of windows, second door in garage leads directly into laundry room, kitchen with coffered ceiling and stainless steel appliances, plantation shutters, coat closet and pantry in hallway, pull down attic stairs, outdoor lighting, reinforced garage door. The outdoor living in this home is what every Florida should have! Large pool with spa, picturesque palm trees, plenty of covered area for dining, sliding glass doors from the diningroom, kitchen, family room and master bedroom! Large potted plants on lanai to stay with home!
